248
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:34,200
Please be quiet.

249
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,480
Look, he's still alive!

250
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:38,720
He's still alive.

251
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,560
Ma'am, please give way.

252
00:11:39,560 --> 00:11:40,240
- Ma'am, let me check on him.
