271
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:10,280
No, he's not dead!

272
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:11,200
I know how you feel.

273
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:12,080
Let's see.

274
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:13,000
How about this?

275
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,680
