414
00:17:52,520 --> 00:17:53,200
You are who you are.

415
00:17:53,320 --> 00:17:54,240
Your father was who he was.

416
00:17:55,360 --> 00:17:56,160
Like I just said,

417
00:17:57,320 --> 00:17:58,880
